modules.description: Handles WebSocket connections by processing incoming streams and establishing communication channels. It works with HTTP streams and WebSocket descriptors to manage message input and output. This module is used to implement real-time communication features like chat services or live data updates over WebSocket connections.

Handles WebSocket connection setup and message handling using HTTP streams and WebSocket descriptors. It enables bidirectional communication for applications like real-time chat or live notifications by processing incoming data and managing send/receive operations.
